title: Justin Bieber is the big winner at MTV EMAs with 5 awards
text: Entertainment Justin Bieber is the big winner at MTV EMAs with 5 awards Canadian singer Justin Bieber poses with his awards during the MTV EMA awards at the Assago forum in Milan, Italy, on Oct 25, 2015. Photo: Reuters Canadian singer Justin Bieber holds the "Best Male" award during the MTV EMA awards at the Assago forum in Milan, Italy, on Octo 25, 2015. Photo: Reuters Justin Bieber, right, and Martin Garrix pose for photographers during a photo call at the 2015 MTV European Music Awards in Milan, Italy on Oct 25, 2015. Photo: AP Justin Bieber arrives for the 2015 MTV European Music Awards in Milan, Italy, on Oct 25, 2015. Photo: AP Ruby Rose releases fire at the start of the start of the MTV European Music Awards in Milan, Italy, on Oct 25, 2015. Photo: AP Pharrell Williams, left, and Helen Lasichanh arrive for the 2015 MTV European Music Awards in Milan, Italy on Oct 25, 2015. Photo: AP
